Subject: drm: bridge: dw-hdmi: Constify mode argument to dw_hdmi_phy_ops
Git-commit: 35a395f1134bbbd2984dcca28c04f09fbbb8b0a4
Patch-mainline: v5.9-rc1
References: jsc#SLE-12680, jsc#SLE-12880, jsc#SLE-12882, jsc#SLE-12883, jsc#SLE-13496, jsc#SLE-15322
